milestones.description: Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes (10) in ODIs for WI, going past Clive Lloyd's 9
Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes (10) in ODIs, going past Clive Lloyd's 9
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (18) for WI, going past Deryck Murray
England's 3-run win against West Indies is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 9-run win against New Zealand
